<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06069a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06069a">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06069a"> 69(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> four tissue papers &mdash; count / to wipe mouth</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">D&eacute;tail que je consignais tout en &eacute;coutant ces explica-tions: Dans la poche de chaque tablier, l&apos;enfant poss&egrave;de des carr&eacute;s de papier de soie dans lesquels <mark>il se mouche proprement</mark>, allant avec gentillesse jeter ensuite le papier souill&eacute; dans une bo&icirc;te munie d&apos;un couvercle l&eacute;ger qu&apos;on soul&egrave;ve ais&eacute;ment. La premi&egrave;re distribution de <mark>ces deux &agrave; quatre petits papiers</mark> remis le matin &agrave; chaque enfant est d&apos;un comique charmant. <font color="green">[Detail that I recorded while listening to these explications: In the pocket of each apron, the child has squares of tissue paper in which it wipes cleanly, then throws the stained paper in a box provided a light cover that can easily be lifted. The first distribution of these two to four little papers given in the morning to each child is a charming scene.]</font> <small> ?. ?, <a name="LARA" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#LARA"><cite title="source">La Revue Philantropique</cite></a> (????) 234</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
